{"word":"H1672 - דָּאַג - dâʼag - daw-ag' - Be afraid","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">דָּאַג</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>dâʼag"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>daw-ag'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Be afraid"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கவலைப்படு, விசாரப்படு, பயப்படு, ஐபப்படு, வருத்தப்படு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to fear, to be anxious, to be concerned, to be afraid, to be careful (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to be anxious, to be concerned"},{"paragraph":"2) to fear, to dread"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; <i>be anxious: - </i>be afraid (careful, sorry), sorrow, take thought."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1672 - דָּאַג - dâʼag - daw-ag'/1672\">H1672</a>, <a href=\"#/H1673 - דֹּאֵג - Dôʼêg - do-ayg'/1673\">H1673</a>, <a href=\"#/H1674 - דְּאָגָה - dᵉʼâgâh - deh-aw-gaw'/1674\">H1674</a>"}]}